Flickr Photo Search

A CakePHP App that lets you search for Flickr photos

REQUIREMENTS
------------

Flickr Photo Search requires CakePHP 2.0 (https://github.com/cakephp/cakephp/tree/2.0)

INSTALLATION
------------

Replace your app directory with the app directory in this repo

CONFIGURATION
---------------

Update app/config/database.php with the value of your Flickr API Key

    public $default = array(
        'datasource' => 'FlickrPhotoSource',
        'key' => 'your_flickr_api_key'
    );

